current_commit_message: Add helper excelCellOrCellRangeRef() to make it easier on calling code to end up generating a valid Excel cell / cell-range reference.
ruff format
When calculating custom periods for a given year, derive the end of the custom period from the default period end using dateutil.relativedelta.relativedelta as it correctly handles leap years.
